      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 48 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 48 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：井泥不食，舊井无禽。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows a well so muddy that men will not drink of it; or an old well to which neither birds (nor other creatures) resort.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
