      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：井谷射鮒，瓮敝漏。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows a well from which by a hole the water escapes and flows away to the shrimps (and such small creatures among the grass), or one the water of which leaks away from a broken basket.</seg>
      </tuv>
